{"tid":1833656,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Ｔ細胞免疫療法 可望「通殺」癌症","createTime":"2020-01-22T04:07:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T04:35:09.000Z","uid":64191,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d510d4be0d124c96d8c1bc6b28faa79760bc884b","tid":1833656,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:07:25.000Z","msg":"〔編譯周虹汶／綜合報導〕繼「嵌合抗原受體Ｔ細胞療法」（CART-T）近兩年成為血液淋巴腫瘤患者的劃時代救星，英國卡迪夫大學研究團隊廿日透過《自然&mdash;免疫學》（Nature Immunology）期刊公布「潛力龐大」的新免疫療法，同樣利用生物工程改造癌症病患的Ｔ細胞來治病，而且可進階「通殺」多種癌症，包括CART-T尚無解的實質固態瘤。<br />\n<br />\n免疫系統是生物體的疾病防禦系統，可保護生物體免受感染，也能殺死癌細胞；屬於淋巴細胞的Ｔ細胞，在當中佔有重要地位，它表面的Ｔ細胞受體（TCR）負責識別由主要組織相容性複合體（MHC）所呈遞的抗原，亦即找出可誘發免疫反應的物質。<br />\n<br />\n揪出多種癌細胞 不會攻擊健康細胞<br />\n<br />\nCART-T療法由前述概念發展而來，但它取出患者血液樣本的Ｔ細胞、加以編輯再放回體內後，僅能識別血液淋巴腫瘤，且它的TCR是因人而異的人類白血球抗原（HLA）。卡迪夫大學研究團隊則運用搭配「Cas9蛋白」的基因剔除技術「常間回文重複序列叢集關聯蛋白系統」（CRISPR），發現新的TCR&mdash;人體正常及癌細胞表面皆有的MR1。<br />\n<br />\n尚未進入人體試驗 安全性仍待確認<br />\n<br />\nMR1和HLA一樣，改造後可識別癌細胞，但不會因人而異，意味可望成就更廣泛的Ｔ細胞療法；目前已額外揪出肺癌、黑色素瘤、白血病、大腸癌、乳癌、攝護腺癌、骨癌、卵巢癌的癌細胞，且不攻擊健康細胞的表面抗原，成功保留了正常組織的原貌。<br />\n<br />\n卡迪夫大學研究人員在實驗室做過人體細胞試驗及動物試驗後，興奮地說這項「非傳統」的新發現「潛力龐大」，但目前尚未進入人體試驗階段，安全性有待確認。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1347669\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1347669&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmA6WLWD%2BvnO7xCw116w%2BR6c%3D&h=516682ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fpaper%2F1347669&h=99c1d08c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/paper/1347669</a>"},{"pid":"c54afa26d1556145e5fd6feec4487dfaef3d1e87","tid":1833656,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:08:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/61yz7b4oHDL._AC_SL1200_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F61yz7b4oHDL._AC_SL1200_.jpg&h=90c7e258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45291a778120897eb627f29edc4b76b3077e0f67","tid":1833656,"uid":133450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:08:50.000Z","msg":"t virus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c076b2f7b2b1f0133df4732ffc589a5b1d7a8d","tid":1833656,"uid":259813,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:10:38.000Z","msg":"原諒我毒，但我個腦浮現左工作細胞個Killer T<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87cff8ee870b3a822873c4e07309b3a51406881b","tid":1833656,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45291a778120897eb627f29edc4b76b3077e0f67","tid":1833656,"uid":133450,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:08:50.000Z","msg":"t virus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:26:56.000Z","msg":"以毒攻毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed52e8ca0aed83dc2245e78fa7d69a97da212d2a","tid":1833656,"uid":186072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:27:41.000Z","msg":"掉落地下爆開佢<br />\n由佢跟空氣傳播<br />\n幾年後全世界就無癌症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8253cc97ab148160ecba51197522f0e839e6c172","tid":1833656,"uid":75326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:35:09.000Z","msg":"同 I Am Legend 開頭一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ai0cYsV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAi0cYsV.jpg&h=c2171c07&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}